fwiw this helmet currently has the best score from the Virginia Tech helmet testing lab of all the MTB helmets they&apos;ve tested (and they&apos;ve tested a lot).

their tests ... &quot;Our bicycle helmet impact tests evaluate a helmet&apos;s ability to reduce linear acceleration and rotational velocity of the head resulting from a range of impacts a cyclist might experience.&quot;

This is a highly respected testing lab. They also test helmets for other sports like Hockey, Football, etc.
